  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      - To evaluate the feasibility of combination chemotherapies comprising of
      gemcitabine-dexamethasone-oxaliplatin for patients with refractory or relapsed malignant
      non-Hodgkin lymphoma (NHL)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      - The feasibility will be evaluated in terms of objective response rate, efficacy of stem
      cell collection, disease-free survival, and overall survival.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
